{"book": 24, "chapter": 49, "sections": [{"type": "heading", "heading": "耶和華審判亞捫"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "論亞捫人。耶和華如此說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 以色列沒有兒子嗎？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "沒有後嗣嗎？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 瑪勒堪為何得迦得之地為業呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "屬他的民為何住其中的城邑呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "日子將到，我必使人聽見打仗的喊聲，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "是攻擊亞捫人拉巴的喊聲。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 拉巴要成為亂堆；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "屬她的鄉村要被火焚燒。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "先前得以色列地為業的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "此時以色列倒要得他們的地為業。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這是耶和華說的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 希實本哪，你要哀號，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為愛地變為荒場。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 拉巴的居民哪，要呼喊，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "以麻布束腰；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "要哭號，在籬笆中跑來跑去；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因瑪勒堪和屬他的祭司、"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "首領要一同被擄去。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "背道的民哪，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你們為何因有山谷，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "就是水流的山谷誇張呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "為何倚靠財寶說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "誰能來到我們這裏呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "主－萬軍之耶和華說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我要使恐嚇從四圍的人中臨到你們；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你們必被趕出，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "各人一直前往，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "沒有人收聚逃民。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "後來我還要使被擄的亞捫人歸回。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這是耶和華說的。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "耶和華審判以東"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "論以東。萬軍之耶和華如此說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 提幔中再沒有智慧嗎？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "明哲人不再有謀略嗎？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們的智慧盡歸無有嗎？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 底但的居民哪，要轉身逃跑，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "住在深密處；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為我向以掃追討的時候，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "必使災殃臨到他。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "摘葡萄的若來到他那裏，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "豈不剩下些葡萄呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "盜賊若夜間而來，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "豈不毀壞直到夠了呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我卻使以掃赤露，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "顯出他的隱密處；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他不能自藏。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他的後裔、弟兄、鄰舍盡都滅絕；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他也歸於無有。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你撇下孤兒，我必保全他們的命；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你的寡婦可以倚靠我。"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華如此說：「原不該喝那杯的一定要喝。你能盡免刑罰嗎？你必不能免，一定要喝！」 "}, {"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華說：「我指着自己起誓，波斯拉必令人驚駭、羞辱、咒詛，並且荒涼。她的一切城邑必變為永遠的荒場。」"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我從耶和華那裏聽見信息，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "並有使者被差往列國去，說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你們聚集來攻擊以東，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "要起來爭戰。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我使你在列國中為最小，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "在世人中被藐視。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "住在山穴中據守山頂的啊，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "論到你的威嚇，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你因心中的狂傲自欺；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你雖如大鷹高高搭窩，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我卻從那裏拉下你來。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這是耶和華說的。"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "「以東必令人驚駭；凡經過的人就受驚駭，又因她一切的災禍嗤笑。 "}, {"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華說：必無人住在那裏，也無人在其中寄居，要像所多瑪、蛾摩拉，和鄰近的城邑傾覆的時候一樣。 "}, {"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "仇敵必像獅子從約旦河邊的叢林上來，攻擊堅固的居所。轉眼之間，我要使以東人逃跑，離開這地。誰蒙揀選，我就派誰治理這地。誰能比我呢？誰能給我定規日期呢？有何牧人能在我面前站立得住呢？ "}, {"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你們要聽耶和華攻擊以東所說的謀略和他攻擊提幔居民所定的旨意。仇敵定要將他們羣眾微弱的拉去，定要使他們的居所荒涼。 "}, {"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "因他們仆倒的聲音，地就震動。人在紅海那裏必聽見呼喊的聲音。 "}, {"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "仇敵必如大鷹飛起，展開翅膀攻擊波斯拉。到那日，以東的勇士心中疼痛如臨產的婦人。」"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "耶和華審判大馬士革"}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "論大馬士革。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 哈馬和亞珥拔蒙羞，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因他們聽見凶惡的信息就消化了。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "海上有憂愁，不得平靜。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 大馬士革發軟，轉身逃跑。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "戰兢將她捉住；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "痛苦憂愁將她抓住，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "如產難的婦人一樣。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我所喜樂可稱讚的城，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "為何被撇棄了呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "她的少年人必仆倒在街上；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "當那日，一切兵丁必默默無聲。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這是萬軍之耶和華說的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我必在大馬士革城中使火着起，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "燒滅便‧哈達的宮殿。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "審判基達和夏瑣城"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "論巴比倫王尼布甲尼撒所攻打的基達和夏瑣的諸國。耶和華如此說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 迦勒底人哪，起來上基達去，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "毀滅東方人。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他們的帳棚和羊羣都要奪去，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "將幔子和一切器皿，並駱駝為自己掠去。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "人向他們喊着說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "四圍都有驚嚇。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 夏瑣的居民哪，要逃奔遠方，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "住在深密處；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為巴比倫王尼布甲尼撒設計謀害你們，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "起意攻擊你們。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 迦勒底人哪，起來！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "上安逸無慮的居民那裏去；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們是無門無閂、獨自居住的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 32, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他們的駱駝必成為掠物；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 32, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們眾多的牲畜必成為擄物。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 32, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我必將剃周圍頭髮的人分散四方，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 32, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使災殃從四圍臨到他們。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 32, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這是耶和華說的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 32, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 33, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 夏瑣必成為野狗的住處，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 33, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "永遠淒涼；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 33, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "必無人住在那裏，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 33, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "也無人在其中寄居。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "耶和華審判以攔"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 33, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 34, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 猶大王西底家登基的時候，耶和華論以攔的話臨到先知耶利米說："}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 34, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 35, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "「萬軍之耶和華如此說：我必折斷以攔人的弓，就是他們為首的權力。 "}, {"verseNum": 36, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我要使四風從天的四方颳來，臨到以攔人，將他們分散四方。這被趕散的人沒有一國不到的。」 "}, {"verseNum": 37, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華說：「我必使以攔人在仇敵和尋索其命的人面前驚惶；我也必使災禍，就是我的烈怒臨到他們，又必使刀劍追殺他們，直到將他們滅盡。 "}, {"verseNum": 38, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我要在以攔設立我的寶座，從那裏除滅君王和首領。這是耶和華說的。"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 38, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 39, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "「到末後，我還要使被擄的以攔人歸回。這是耶和華說的。」"}]}]}